ZH: 春天是四季中最美好的季节。
EN: Spring is the most beautiful season of the year.

ZH: 春天来了，大地开始变绿。
EN: Spring has arrived, and the earth is turning green.

ZH: 春天的阳光温暖而明媚。
EN: The sunshine in spring is warm and bright.

ZH: 春天的花朵绽放着美丽的色彩。
EN: The flowers in spring bloom in beautiful colors.

ZH: 春天是万物复苏的季节。
EN: Spring is the season of rejuvenation for all things.

ZH: 春天的空气清新宜人。
EN: The air in spring is fresh and pleasant.

ZH: 春天是踏青的好时节。
EN: Spring is a good time for outings.

ZH: 春天的风吹来了花香。
EN: The wind in spring brings the fragrance of flowers.

ZH: 春天的天空湛蓝如洗。
EN: The sky in spring is clear and blue.

ZH: 春天的雨水润泽大地。
EN: The spring rain moistens the earth.

ZH: 春天是草长莺飞的季节。
EN: Spring is the season when grass grows and birds sing.

ZH: 春天的阳光让人感到愉快。
EN: The sunshine in spring makes people feel happy.

ZH: 春天的气候变化多端。
EN: The weather in spring changes frequently.

ZH: 春天的草地上开满了鲜花。
EN: The grassland in spring is full of blooming flowers.

ZH: 春天的温暖拂过脸庞。
EN: The warmth of spring brushes across the face.

ZH: 春天是播种的时节。
EN: Spring is the season for planting.

ZH: 春天是生机勃勃的季节。
EN: Spring is a vibrant season.

ZH: 春天的树木发芽了。
EN: The trees in spring start to sprout.

ZH: 春天是户外活动的好时光。
EN: Spring is a good time for outdoor activities.
